'''Katie Purvis''' (born [[1966]]) is an actress who played the "Maternal Ewok" in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. She is also the daughter of ''Star Wars'' actor [[Jack Purvis]], and is good friends with [[Maureen Charlton]].

==Biography==
Katie became a part of the ''Star Wars'' saga with her role in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']], where she portrayed the [[Parent|Maternal]] Ewok who held a [[wokling]] in her [[Limb|arms]]. Her father and many other actors of short stature were featured in that scene.

